{"tid":1048167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度被飛俘機師歸國民英雄  「八字鬍」掀模仿熱潮","createTime":"2019-03-05T12:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T18:10:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0da999273196a3be1452bb9fbaf87b9c5d2610f2","tid":1048167,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3935/d3935454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3935%2Fd3935454.jpg&h=0d89d1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3935/d3935455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3935%2Fd3935455.jpg&h=c123d13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「阿比南丹鬍」在印度掀起熱潮。（圖／路透）<br />\n<br />\n記者錢玉紘／綜合報導<br />\n印度與巴基斯坦在上月27日爆發空襲戰，印度空軍（IAF）飛行員阿比南丹（Abhinandan Varthaman）也在當天遭到俘虜，2天後被釋放回到印度。阿比南丹回國之後，被視為英雄，印度國內更掀起了一波「阿比南丹」八字鬍的模仿熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n阿比南丹在1日下午被巴基斯坦釋放，步行走過印巴邊界，正式回到印度，結果他的鬍子也意外在國內掀起風潮，阿比南丹留著八字鬍，但下方繼續延伸到臉頰上，形狀非常特殊，許多印度男性特別把鬍子修成這個形狀，還把照片上傳到網路上，寫著「受阿比南丹鼓勵」、「向英雄致敬」、「為我們的士兵感到驕傲」。<br />\n<br />\n印巴兩國在27日發生衝突，一架印度的米格21的戰機在遭到巴國擊落，當時在機上的阿比南丹彈射出去保命，之後巴國的網路上流傳他雙手被綑在身後，遭到一群人帶走的影像，另一支影片則是他受訪的片段，雖然眼睛腫起來，但是語氣平靜且堅定，並拒絕回答任何有關軍事任務的問題。<br />\n<br />\n阿比南丹冷靜應對的影像在網路上廣為流傳，不管是印度或巴基斯坦人民都受到感動，更有許多人在網路上貼出他照片，用以呼籲和平。<br />\n<br />\n阿比南丹在1日獲釋，他身穿藍色西裝外套、白色襯衫以及灰色長褲，通過印巴兩國邊界瓦加（Attari-Wagah），帶著微笑走回印度，邊界地區也有上百位民眾聚集，揮舞旗子並放著音樂，熱烈歡迎阿比南丹，隨後更掀起一波鬍子熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n▼阿比南丹冷靜應對，印巴兩國民眾都受到激勵。（圖／路透）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3935/d3935453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3935%2Fd3935453.jpg&h=074cd8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 印度飛官遭俘...歸國後變全民英雄！「酷炫八字鬍」掀模仿熱潮 | ETtoday國際 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190305/1391608.htm#ixzz5hIhbeX6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190305%2F1391608.htm%23ixzz5hIhbeX6g&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXvZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=734bac84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190305/1391608.htm#ixzz5hIhbeX6g</a>"},{"pid":"6a22f02af25d66d76c640b78f31791faa23bbd72","tid":1048167,"uid":38904,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"俾渣過佢嘅國家炸落嚟都好意思叫英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3570f15a583b032b6b42ffa7d4d8c53a013fa723","tid":1048167,"uid":26601,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"原來白事當紅事搞係d 所謂文明古國既一貫手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0076f4cb8a2ceef546075f92b36161407dcf67","tid":1048167,"uid":36134,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"印度d國家主義好似仲勁過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108b159192d636fef747126fb295d9572ced8f3b","tid":1048167,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"米格21<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c9097cb073eb4a6cd309133b947994183eb196","tid":1048167,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e0076f4cb8a2ceef546075f92b36161407dcf67","tid":1048167,"uid":36134,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"印度d國家主義好似仲勁過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"咁大個國家唔玩呢d點管到"},{"pid":"4b59f4ccb03c5979efe0aa674aac4438306508af","tid":1048167,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"108b159192d636fef747126fb295d9572ced8f3b","tid":1048167,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"米格21<img src=\"/assets